commit.message: Added in the ability to see vibes that have already been answered. Fixed a visual bug. Changed thumbnail aesthetic.
Added icons for iPad, new galleries on the first floor.
Small text change on score cash in. Bluetooth only in use. Line divider auto layout fix.
Auto layout for high score cell.
Auto layout for the correct/incorrect screen.
Auto layout submit vibe screen
Auto layout for vibe writing.
Auto layout for the answer selection, or for art selection for vibe writing.
Auto layout for Vibe Page. Had to remix the view layout to avoid pageviewcontroller odd behavior.
Autolayout for points cashed in screen
Auto layout for "how to play"
Gallery browse auto layout
Score screen auto layout
Bluetooth addition for nearby galleries

New assets, random bubble images. UI Polish, points gained displayed on finish, swipe indicator, changes to font color, new thread lines and backgrounds. Bluetooth integration for nearby galleries. Recolored reload symbol. Fixes to lame/rude behavior. Profanity filtering. New notification flow on submit vibe to be more explicit. Capping language on writing vibes. no empty strings allowed on vibes. Copy changes. New help screen, and corresponding info buttons. New "cash-in points" behavior to make vibe points gathered over time explicit, in both vibe and point origin (regular/bonus). Fixes to multiple images. New library Fingertips for touch down graphic for demo recording. Launch screen. Transparency bug on navigation controller push. Activity spinners on art grid cells.
Tint changes, some new rooms added, badge numbers, new asset usage.

Data integration of correct/incorrect, and clever/lame numbers from content server. Organizing and sorting vibes based on a mix of fresh/clever. High score board updates wth dataset and shows the status of the various vibes. numerous UI improvements and polish. Curated room list. Fixes to personally created vibes, vibes already solved. Fixes to version updating with interaction with contentful. Loading spinners and completion block based flow on upload dependent screen. Denying lame vibes from the data set. Re-arranged vibe write view to have better layout.

UI reworks, new screen flow, new data scheme usage of UUIds for persistent record keeping. persistent local score.
Refresh mechanics, new imagery. Indicator to show fresh content. ways to write vibes when none exist. new wip high score table.
Interaction with contentful server. Cleaned up PMA data. Basic A-Z interaction on solving/posting vibes.
Initial Commit
